  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c4e8a1f9d0b24e5a8c3f2d1b0e9a7c6d, type: 3}
  m_Name: Leander
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  EventText: You can barely make out a man swimming through stormy waters in the
    dark of night. When you offer help he refuses, explaining he crosses the strait
    to see his forbidden love. Across the strait you see a torch burning atop a tower,
    lit by his love to guide him. You wonder if a single light is enough to guide
    one through the night.
  BackgroundImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 22da5e11d909a524ea70fc2e04323aa6, type: 3}
  ImageStartingPosition: {x: 12.5, y: 25.5}
  ImageStartingScale: {x: 18, y: 18, z: 1}
  SummaryPosition: 0
  Options:
  - OptionText: You will be the third to hope for his safe arrival on the shore\n(Gain
      Rituals)
    Outcome:
      OutcomeType: 3
      RewardInfo:
      - AphroditeMajor
      - PoseidonMajor
  - OptionText: You have seen how these stories often end\n(Gain Cards)
    Outcome:
      OutcomeType: 1
      RewardInfo:
      - Drown
      - Drown
